We are part of some networks of association at local level:&#xd;
- "Rete delle Associazioni" of the Municipality of Catania - here some notes on its mission: http://www.comune.catania.it/informazioni/cstampa/default.aspx?cs=23683 &#xd;
- "Fabbrica del Decoro" of the Municipality of Catania - here some notes on its mission: http://catania.livesicilia.it/2015/04/01/nasce-fabbrica-del-decoro-cantiere-per-rigenerazione-urbana_334836/&#xd;
Currently we are enhancing the relation with some NGOs collaborating with them sometimes as in the case of our latest cooperation with EUCA for the presentation of a project candidate in the Europe for Citizens programme, unfortunately not approved. A part of EUCA we are in relation with some other organizations. It is possible verify at this link http://www.europe-hopes.eu/#!/Friends, even if the list is not exhaustive.&#xd;
In the workplan 2016-2017 is foreseen to establish formal partnership with our current friends and to take part to at least one network at european level aimed to active european citizenship.
